    {
      "id": "1909e267-a4dc-43a5-8307-69a1eafad770",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose a model that adapts to growing pools of concepts and/or questions. The model, called ARAIKT rpeserves previous representations while being able to adapt to increasing concepts and question banks. ",
